'Use page pagination and remove auto rows per page option.',
'</p>',
'<p>The end result is something that is missing out on many of the nice features',
'of IG but at least it is editable and shows multiple lines of text only where needed.',
'There are plans (no promise if or when) for a future relase of IG to support fixed or variable height rows.',
'</p>',
'<p>Customizations:<br>',
