'hidden column could be used to determine the highlight class value or it could',
'even be the class name thus moving the logic onto the server.',
'2) The Selection Actions menu has two new items Mark and Un-mark. Selecting ',
'some records and choosing Mark will add a bold text style to the row. ',
'Selecting Un-mark will remove the bold style. This is done with actions that',
'act on the currently selected records.',
'</p>',
'<p>Programmatically modifying the highlight metadata property can interfere with',
'the Highlight feature. The Mark and Un-mark actions will remember and restore',
'report setting highlights. The cell style based on ONLEAVE overrides any ',
'column report setting highlights. Users may find this confusing. You could',
'change the logic so that if there is already a highlight property no change is',
'made. Or you could disable the highlight feature.',
'</p>',
'<p>Demonstrates:<br>',
'Updating model metadata. Responding to model notifications.',
'Defining IG actions. Adding to grid Selection Actions menu.',
'<br>Customizations:<br>',
