'<p>A few people have been frustrated by not being able to select text from an ',
'IG to copy to the clipboard. See <a href="https://community.oracle.com/message/14391189" ',
' target="_blank">here</a> for example.',
'</p>',
'<p>Copy text to the clipboard works with an Interactive Report because that is just a plain table',
'so normal browser text seleciton worls. In contrast IG is an advanced grid widget',
'that is used to select rows and edit. Just as the select form element doesn''t ',
'support text selection neither does IG. There are technical reasons why the mouse',
'down event used to select text would interfere with the IG behavior.',
'</p>',
'<p>This page demonstrates how to work around this by copying the selected',
'rows to the clipboard. It uses browser clipboard APIs that are not finalized',
'standards and vary across browsers. It does not work on all browsers.',
'This will hopefully be built in to IG in a future version of APEX</p>',
'',
'<p>Demonstrates:<br>',
'Using clipboard event and API to copy IG selection to clipboard. Select some rows,',
'right click and choose Copy or press Ctrl+C.<br>',
'Customizations:<br>',
'See Page attribute JavaScript: Function and Global Variable Declaration to add ',
'copy to selection action menu. ',
'Dynamic Action copy on body that handles the copy event. IG Advanced: JavaScript Code ',
'to add the copy action.<br>',
'Issues:<br>',
