'instantiating a grid widget that borrows almost all of its options from',
'the grid widget in the IG. Extra code is added to keep column widths, order, and visibility in sync. ',
'Adding filters or changing the sort order applies to both views.',
'</p>',
'<p>Customizations:<br>',
'All the work is done in page attribute Function and Global Variable Declaration.',
'<br>Issues<br>',
'The report settings area doesn''t resize the view area as its size changes. ',
'This has nothing to do with multiple views.<br>',
'Would be nice if in the future the reportsettingschange event included info about',
'what settings changed to the syncing of views is only done when needed.',
